She is the second in line to the norwegian throne, following her father Crown  Prince Haakon, and King Harald.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ChW82zN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For her 18th birthday, she got a tour of the parliament...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Asmbtyz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...the supreme court of Norway...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DnLRUJK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>...and a visit to the prime minister. Thus, visiting the three branches of government in Norway: The legislative, executive and judicial.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U6OhjmU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The day she becomes queen, she will also be the highest ranking in the norwegian military. Leading up to her 18th birthday, she also visited the military.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YKnCT3A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>..where she also got to fly a fighter jet. (Yes, she was in control of the plane for a while.)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/notP4pM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They grow up so fast. Happy birthday!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/D4RuYIN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[frosketosk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tell us how you really feel Mitch.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/55kDPmR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xvnbfKU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/55kDPmR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DaShanghaiKid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I like everything about this</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aCu